  body
    header
      span#preLogo  
      a(href='http://www.digitalharborfoundation.org')
        img.smallLogo(src='smallDHFLogo.svg', alt='Digital Harbor Foundation')
      span#postLogo project
      a(href='http://www.edtechlink.org/')
        #anchorLogo
          | We link learners to doers
    section#subHeader
      h1 #edpain
      p
        | identifying the 
        a(href='http://www.waywordradio.org/pain_point/', target='_blank') pain points
        |  of education
    section#description
      p
        | This wall is an open 
        a(href='http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/', target='_blank') cc 3.0
        |  platform for teachers, students, admins, policy makers, parents, and technologists to constructively identify 
        a(href='http://www.waywordradio.org/pain_point/', target='_blank') pain points
        |  in education.
    section#painEntry
      p
        | I'm a
        span.pluralRole n
        input.role(type='text', placeholder='teacher, student, parent, etc.', maxlength="30")
        | and I have an 
        a(href='https://twitter.com/#!/search/%23edpain', target='_blank') #edpain
        | :
      p.description
        textarea(maxlength='300')
      p.identifiers
        | My name is
        input.name(type='text', maxlength="50")
        | from
        input.zip(type='text', placeholder='zip code', maxlength="5")
        |  .
      button.post post your edpain
    section#postPainEntry
      p Thank you for sharing your #edpain.
      button.back Have another edpain?
    section#pains
      h2 edpains
      ul
    footer
      p Loading more edpains...
      button Load more edpains